About Our Firm




Consistent Strategy
We look for opportunities to invest with significant downside protection and compelling upside to generate superior returns.




Opportunistic Focus
We take a creative approach toward deal structuring to accommodate the unique needs of each transaction and seller.




Value-Driven Control Investments
We invest in high quality businesses in special or proprietary situations where we can leverage our team’s experience to deliver value for our investors.




Growth Capital Investments
We are late stage investors in high growth, high potential industries.  We invest from $25 million to over $1 billion in transactions.






 
 
 






 
 
 




